					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10269373#post-4149267</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10269373/scp-3596#post-4149267</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 11 Feb 2019 05:25:36 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>DrChandra</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1956625</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Slight nitpick regarding the requirements:</p> <ul> <li>A male of African-American descent</li> <li>A person of Asian descent</li> </ul> <p>Since this only occurs in Japan, which is extremely ethnically homogenous, the large majority of candidates would be Asian regardless, and an African American would be extremely rare, especially if you do mean an African American and not just someone of African descent.</p> <p>But if you're going to use Amerian actors and splice it with Japanese stock footage, that makes more sense.</p> <p>Other than that, a decent overall article.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
