					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10269373#post-4148765</guid>
				<title>Foundation Sentai</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10269373/scp-3596#post-4148765</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 10 Feb 2019 19:02:47 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>IAmTheOoga</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3942052</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I'm back, baby.</p> <p>I don't know how I was able to capture the feeling of nostalgia for something that I wasn't around for, but it worked out in the end so whatevs. Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1404533&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1549909296" alt="Zyn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1404533)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" >Zyn</a></span> fyor confirming that this idea didn't suck big macaroni, and PopcornK in chat for giving the go-ahead to post.</p> <p>But yeah, this marks the end of my burnout. Expect more good/bad things to come out of the hellscape that is my sandbox.</p> <p>Also, fun fact: The Nakajima events were named after the original Godzilla suit actor, Haruo Nakajima.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
